<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Heinrich Uehlfelder an Eberhard von Eberstein, Hauptmann Bischof Johanns I. von Würzburg</head><p>Heinrich Uehlfelder teilt wegen Albrecht von der Kere mit, dass er in den nächsten acht Tagen kommen wird.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_216" id="107v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_216_r1l13"><expan>Eb<ex>er</ex>hart</expan> <expan>Eb<ex>er</ex>ſtein</expan> meins <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r1l14">von vvirtʒburg hawbtman </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_216_r1l15">Mein dinſt cʒevor <expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> Eberhart / Als du mir <expan>verſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r1l16">haſt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Ker <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / Laʒʒ ıch dich vviſſen / daʒ ıch 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ıch </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r1l17">danyden ʒeſchıcken han / vnd in den <expan>nehſt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Acht tagen <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r1l18">hin ab <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wird / vnd ſo main ich <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> alſo mit dir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r1l19">von den ſachen <expan>cʒered<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>Sup<ex>ra</ex></expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r1l20">von <expan>heintʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r1l21">V̈ltfelder </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_216" id="107v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Eb<ex>er</ex>hart</expan>
<expan>Eb<ex>er</ex>stein</expan>, meins <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von
                        Wirczburg hawbtman </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Mein dinst czevor. <expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Eberhart, als du mir
                                <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hast <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Ker <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, lazz ich dich
                        wissen, daz ich danyden zeschicken han und in den
                            <expan>nehst<ex>e</ex>n</expan> acht tagen
                            <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> hin ab <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wird; und so main ich <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> also mit dir von den
                        sachen <expan>czered<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                            <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>. <lb/>Von <expan>Heincze<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Ültfelder.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
